ypology.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aEddasxHistory and criticism. 0aEnglish literatureyOld English, ca. 450-1100xHistory and criticism. 0aFolklore in literature. 0aMythology, Norse, in literature. 0aOld Norse literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aStorytellers in literature. 4aMittelalter. 4aSkandinavien. 4aThul. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aMiddle Ages.  aScandinavia.  aThul.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2016z9783110485264oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831104563250 cprintz978311045562540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311045730840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110457308423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110457308/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DKUb2016